description: This common Anurak purrs with a rating of 22, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 66, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Stringalong for East, 5 for South, and Leverage for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [66 Votes, Common]
